{"title":"新年我在北京给娘写信","authors":["彭学明"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":1,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新年我在北京给娘写信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彭学明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又过年了娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿在北京给您写信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"异乡的笔墨就这么善良"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲曲款款"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传送儿子的孝心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有听话不听话的字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在这时集合拢来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等着向您"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾诉衷情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您好吗娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的身板是否还硬朗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您是否还在月下纺那架老车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您是否还在灯前补那个补丁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟升起的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就想起您躬身锄地的姿式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起您青筋突露的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布满乡风和民情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大把大把的土著民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在您沉重的足下生长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民谚和着的汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送您满身黄尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山磨老了您"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水洗瘦了您"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子的月华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让您苦难一生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您种植农业哺育农业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您种植儿子哺育儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您把农业和儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都打扮得朴素而光景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿是您农业最好的庄稼啦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿是您一生最好的收成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子想您白发转青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子想您皱纹抚平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿子想您相依为命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保重娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要站在村口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打望未归的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要翻山越岭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年岁大了腿疼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家红灯高挂时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将是一幅春联贴在家门"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}